text: As many as 130 kg of seas cucumbers were seized by wildlife officials at the Thoothukudi Fishing Harbour on Wednesday. S. Jeyakumar (44) of Nattukottai Chetti Street, Mattakadai, was arrested. Based on a tipoff, the raid was conducted and the sea cucumbers were found in two cartons and as many baskets, said A. Kalidass, Forest Guard.
title: Sea cucumbers seized
